lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41235ace87550ebd0a1bbf70d1967b6c29d08036","tid":511412,"uid":143719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"daee3bfb7e622ddf841f933528f77e26e2650e84","tid":511412,"uid":123956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"咁樓主想點?<br />\n你老豆明顯是欺善怕惡,首先你要有能力獨立,無任何東西是無他不行,住家不是寫他名的話勝面高。<br />\n跟手你要比他強硬和心狠手辣,直接當他敵人咁撚,長期的話一定有效。<br />\n至於他明顯脾氣差,忍得多樓主一是抑鬱一是和他有大衝突,自己諗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"而家讀緊書，嚟緊考慮輟唔輟學，做份正職賺錢搬出去，至於間屋就係佢名嘅，佢話過：&ldquo;咁有本事你搬出去lor&rdquo; 。"},{"pid":"46bcb1fdf301da346a1967ee4835323a1b0a659b","tid":511412,"uid":147541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0435ff7a5cd0fb5939affcbfd25f19ab9879255","tid":511412,"uid":143719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981f3189862af01ac6baafed5a0944f6c160501e","tid":511412,"uid":78885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"考慮報警？ 報黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"提供佢冇還錢嘅證據畀差人，睇可唔可以拉佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 一睇啲句於知樓主係個幾冇腦既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68852ab754a924f6937038df1458695292769f64","tid":511412,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41235ace87550ebd0a1bbf70d1967b6c29d08036","tid":511412,"uid":143719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"daee3bfb7e622ddf841f933528f77e26e2650e84","tid":511412,"uid":123956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"咁樓主想點?<br />\n你老豆明顯是欺善怕惡,首先你要有能力獨立,無任何東西是無他不行,住家不是寫他名的話勝面高。<br />\n跟手你要比他強硬和心狠手辣,直接當他敵人咁撚,長期的話一定有效。<br />\n至於他明顯脾氣差,忍得多樓主一是抑鬱一是和他有大衝突,自己諗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"而家讀緊書，嚟緊考慮輟唔輟學，做份正職賺錢搬出去，至於間屋就係佢名嘅，佢話過：&ldquo;咁有本事你搬出去lor&rdquo; 。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"忍到的忍話要忍到畢業先,拿個好成績。無學歷你什麼都不是,這個時候要諗1-2個職業你是有興趣學有能力做的,咁手放少少錢入金融市場錢滾錢,但注意別讓你老豆知道和有關的信要寄去其他郵箱。"},{"pid":"71fd1f420fd77a425c92d44ffa232e4dac30f582","tid":511412,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f22d6153f397c941fe304b634dd863bb879106","tid":511412,"uid":16061,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"19f949cc68bf05f27c02605706384dc86b49eced","tid":511412,"uid":132262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"咁點解你呀媽會要呢舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"因為佢阿媽都係垃圾囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}